Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.93,0:25:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我认真的  -就带着这些恐怖分子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I mean it. - With a bunch of terrorists?
