Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.06,0:28:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗莎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Roze. Shh, shh, shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.79,0:28:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.13,0:28:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科巴的人抓走了罗让\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Koba's men took Rojan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.04,0:28:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do they want?
