Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.21,0:30:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就必须做好不惧一切排除万难的准备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to do everything without fear, without care.
