Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.93,0:33:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 塔玛兹 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, Tamaz. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.02,0:33:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.58,0:33:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你的工人 工作时长现在是12个小时了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please tell your workers, the shift is now 12 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.30,0:33:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们多送一些 你们多打包一些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We deliver more, you package more.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.38,0:34:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,双赢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Win, win.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.97,0:34:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.73,0:34:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库尔德人那边进行得如何了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How's it progressing with the Kurds?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.36,0:34:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科巴跟我们的矛盾加剧了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Koba's becoming a bigger problem for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.36,0:34:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经控制住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got it under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.61,0:34:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸的女友跟你妈联手了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And your father's girlfriend working with your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.53,0:34:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了我在处理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I said I'm handling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.58,0:34:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,复仇的那扇窗要关上了 肖恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The window to retaliate is closing, Sean.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.03,0:35:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.41,0:35:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you want me to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.44,0:35:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让她也变成我们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you want her to be like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.82,0:35:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我不应该来这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think I shouldn't be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.82,0:35:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能由着性子行事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can do what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.44,0:35:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲好赌 他帮黑手党押注\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My father was a gambler. He ran bets for the mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.95,0:35:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也不想 可他没拒绝的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He didn't want to, but you don't say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.16,0:35:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有天他还是拒绝了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then he said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.46,0:36:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我家厨房被他们爆头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They shot him in the head in our kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.01,0:36:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还打死了我的小弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My little brother too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.05,0:36:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怕他长大寻仇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So he wouldn't grow up and take vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.05,0:36:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早看清了这个世界的模样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know what this world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.81,0:36:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗莎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Roze.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.35,0:36:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有多了解我母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How well do you know my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.15,0:36:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许我了解你不知道的那一面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe I know some things you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.03,0:36:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你肯定知道 她最后会卖了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you'll know that she'll screw you over in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.30,0:36:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉莱 长老们要召集会议了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lale, the elders have called a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.97,0:36:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得谈谈华莱士的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to discuss the Wallaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.73,0:37:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sean.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.98,0:37:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先请\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.96,0:37:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说你们不开心 我能如何效劳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm told you're unhappy. How can I make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.59,0:37:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲的行动 卢安 给我们帮了倒忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The actions of your mother, Luan, this does not help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.39,0:37:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科巴觉察出叛乱的气息 把我们逼得更紧了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Koba smells rebellion, so he pushes us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.73,0:37:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们利润太薄 连寄回家的钱都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is too little profit to send home,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.90,0:37:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们跟城里的其他帮派不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're not the same as others in this city, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.82,0:37:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们夺权是为了自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Those who want power for its own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.99,0:37:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们则是在为祖国人民的自由而战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My people want freedom in our homelands.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.03,0:37:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这里的生意做不下去 像现在这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If our business here fails, as it fails now,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.33,0:37:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会去别的城市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for us there are other cities,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.04,0:38:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找别的营生继续斗争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}other ways to continue the struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.08,0:38:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的生意不会做不下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your business won't fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.00,0:38:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等科巴倒台 你们会在这个城市有一席之地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When Koba's gone, you'll have a place in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.71,0:38:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你们保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I promised you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.67,0:38:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你行动太慢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.35,0:38:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾说过 与科巴同谋就是于我为敌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I said I'd hit anyone who sides with Koba.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.35,0:38:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在看来这句话要升级了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not enough now. It's time to escalate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.61,0:38:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也很想相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'd like to share your confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.44,0:38:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, we need each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.03,0:38:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你更需要我们 没了我们 你就是光杆司令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you need us more. Without us, you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.62,0:38:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会给你们寄回家的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll give you money to send home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.41,0:38:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也会给你们寄回家的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll give you weapons for the fight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.62,0:38:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真有权承诺给我们这些吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These things are yours to give?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.79,0:38:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈有她自己的打算 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your mother has her own ambitions, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.96,0:38:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经说过了 我说到做到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like I said, you have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.68,0:38:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该让我们看到好处了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then let us see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.14,0:40:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.10,0:40:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,街头混混 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Street grunt, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.27,0:40:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手举起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hands up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.15,0:40:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐前排 快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Front seat. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.91,0:40:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你会头一个来杀我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thought I'd be higher up your kill list.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.96,0:40:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧了 有人告诉我你不能碰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Funny. I was told you were off limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.21,0:40:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约瑟夫·辛格 他特别交代过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Joseph Singer. He was very insistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.30,0:41:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你我暂时在同一战线上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Turns out you and I are on the same side. For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.81,0:41:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不在乎你 也不在乎什么辛格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do not give a fuck about you or Singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.07,0:41:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但科巴在乎 尤其你在对他的新朋友痛下杀手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But Koba would. Especially as you've been killing his new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.07,0:41:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到这个了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.45,0:41:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生说再深一根头发丝的距离 我就\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The surgeon said a hair either way and, pff...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.25,0:41:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹啊 真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miracle, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.04,0:41:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我想 他是故意的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then I thought, did he mean to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.76,0:41:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太符合艾略特的风格了 他不想出卖灵魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's very Elliot. Anything for a clean conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.05,0:41:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不客气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.93,0:41:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太会骗人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're such a good liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.56,0:41:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗的自己都信了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You even fall for your own bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.27,0:41:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我申请了最难办的案子 芬恩的案底千头万绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I asked for the worst case, you know. Finn's file was huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.69,0:41:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗钱 勒索 共谋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Money laundering, extortion, conspiracy,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.99,0:42:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故意伤害 虐杀 绑架 贩运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}ABH, GBH, murder, kidnap, trafficking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.78,0:42:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你的案底 却空无一物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yours...was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.50,0:42:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有 也没人在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing. No one cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.33,0:42:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你无关紧要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're an irrelevance.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.00,0:42:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是你爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not your dad
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.92,0:42:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也做不来这些苟且\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you don't know how to do any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.26,0:42:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说完了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.14,0:42:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛格说你又回来了 但你想退出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Singer said you're back in, but you want out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.27,0:42:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好下定决心 你我都知道你来此的真正目的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make your mind up We both know why you're really here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.44,0:42:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩的目标一致\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and I want the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.81,0:42:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把投资人赶出这座城\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To rid this city of the Investors.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.44,0:42:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要么帮我 要么滚蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So either help me or fuck off.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.04,0:42:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开枪吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.00,0:42:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没说错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're right
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.59,0:42:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何必呢 你我共寄一个屋檐下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't have to. You're all hiding under one roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.38,0:43:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要科巴拉莱的地址给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could just give Koba Lale's address,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.80,0:43:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华莱士一家就齐齐整整了 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and that's all the Wallaces in one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.48,0:43:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不在同一战线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're not on the same side.
